      <div class="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-3 gradient-text">
        ASHRU
      </div>
      <p class="muted leading-relaxed">
        An open community standard for token-efficient LLM knowledge-graph extraction.
        Spec public domain (CC0). Reference parsers MIT.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="font-semibold mb-3 text-ink-100">Format</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 muted">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ashru-format/ashru-format/blob/main/SPEC.md" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">v1 Specification</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ashru-format/ashru-format" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Reference Parsers</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ashru-format/ashru-format/tree/main/examples" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Examples</a></li>
        <li><a href="#converter" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Live JSON ↔ ASHRU Converter</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="font-semibold mb-3 text-ink-100">Talk to us</div>
      <p class="muted leading-relaxed text-[0.92rem]">
        Questions, criticisms, ideas — all in the open. Public discussion happens on GitHub.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 muted mt-3">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ashru-format/ashru-format/issues" class="text-accent-300 hover:text-accent-500 font-semibold">→ Open an Issue</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ashru-format/ashru-format/discussions" class="text-accent-300 hover:text-accent-500 font-semibold">→ Join Discussions</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
