      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-ink-300/60">spec v1.0 · release v1.0.0 · 2026-05-06</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/ashru-format/ashru-format" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">github.com/ashru-format</a>
